data.Sentence_cn: 你读了这本书吗？
data.Sentence: Did you read the book?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是我先看了电影。
data.Sentence: Yes, but I saw the film first.

data.Sentence_cn: 我在看了电影以后读了这本书。
data.Sentence: I read the book after I had seen the film.

data.Sentence_cn: 你去看医生了吗？
data.Sentence: Did you go to the doctor?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是我先预约了。
data.Sentence: Yes, but I made an appointment first.

data.Sentence_cn: 我先预约然后去看了医生。
data.Sentence: I went to the doctor after I had made an appointment.

data.Sentence_cn: 老板离开办公室了吗？
data.Sentence: Did the boss leave the office?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是他先完成了工作。
data.Sentence: Yes, but he finished his work first.

data.Sentence_cn: 他完成了工作以后离开了办公室。
data.Sentence: He left the office after he had finished his work.

data.Sentence_cn: 你妻子出去了吗？
data.Sentence: Did your wife go out?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是她先做完了家务。
data.Sentence: Yes, but she finished the housework first.

data.Sentence_cn: 她做完家务以后出了门。
data.Sentence: She went out after she had finished the housework.

data.Sentence_cn: 你的老师给你发练习本了吗？
data.Sentence: Did your teacher give you your exercise book?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，他先改正了错误。
data.Sentence: Yes, but he corrected it first.

data.Sentence_cn: 他改正了以后发给我练习本。
data.Sentence: He gave me my exercise book after he had corrected it.

data.Sentence_cn: 你妹妹去度假了吗？
data.Sentence: Did your sister go on holiday?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是她先参加了考试。
data.Sentence: Yes, but she took the examination first.

data.Sentence_cn: 她参加完考试后去度假了。
data.Sentence: She went on holiday after she had taken the examination.

data.Sentence_cn: 你买了新车吗？
data.Sentence: Did you buy a new car?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是我先卖了旧车。
data.Sentence: Yes, but I sold my old one first.

data.Sentence_cn: 卖了旧车以后我卖了新车。
data.Sentence: I bought a new car after I had sold my old one.

data.Sentence_cn: 你妈妈擦地板了吗？
data.Sentence: Did your mother sweep the floor?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是她先清理了橱柜。
data.Sentence: Yes, but she dusted the cupboard first.

data.Sentence_cn: 清理了橱柜后她擦了地板。
data.Sentence: She swept the floor after she had dusted the cupboard.

data.Sentence_cn: 你喝了牛奶吗？
data.Sentence: Did you drink the milk?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是我先把它煮沸了。
data.Sentence: Yes, but I boiled it first.

data.Sentence_cn: 牛奶煮沸后我才喝。
data.Sentence: I drank the milk after I had boiled it.

data.Sentence_cn: 孩子们上床睡觉了吗？
data.Sentence: Did the children go to bed?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，但是他们先洗了澡。
data.Sentence: Yes, but they had a bath first.

data.Sentence_cn: 孩子们洗完澡后上床睡觉了。
data.Sentence: The children went to bed after they had had a bath.
